title: Computers and Security Volume 23 Issue 8 December 2004-EEn
description:
Time again for a bunch of new releases from the scene. If the name doesn't mean anything to you, you probably don't need it. For those who you who wish to help please add a comment with a short description. 

Remember to read the *.nfo file for installation instructions. 

And! I will only seed as long as necessary, so please stay with the file after download!
